01:29:08,459 --> 01:29:09,709
なーんてね

1612
01:29:15,709 --> 01:29:17,417
（ボタンを押す音）

1613
01:29:37,834 --> 01:29:46,792
♪ Do you remember 
the paths where we met？

1614
